articles.title: Arizona girl Willa Rawlings' body found 2 weeks after storm surge swept her away

articles.title: Arizona dad accused of killing man who tried to enter teen daughter’s restroom stall gets 8-year prison term
articles.description: An Arizona father who authorities say fatally beat a man who allegedly tried to follow the dad’s teenage daughter into a restroom stall was sentenced Friday to eight years in prison.
